OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FThe owner of an XL Bully dog which
OL,7,Fsavaged a man to death has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor three years.
OL,10,FChristopher Bell, 45, previously
OL,11,Fadmitted being the owner of a dog
OL,12,Fwhich caused injury leading to death
OL,13,Fwhile dangerously out of control in a
OL,14,Fpublic place.
OL,16,FIan Langley, 54, was walking his puppy
OL,17,Fin Shiney Row, near Sunderland, when
OL,18,Fhe was attacked by a dog and suffered
OL,19,Ffatal neck injuries on 3 October 2023.
