OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FAt Newcastle Crown Court on Monday (27
OL,7,FJanuary), Bell, who now lives in Hull,
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to three years in prison
OL,9,Fand was banned from keeping dogs.
OL,11,FFollowing the smashing of a window at
OL,12,Fhis home, Bell had run from his
OL,13,Faddress with his two dogs to chase Mr
OL,14,FLangley, who he thought to be
OL,15,Fresponsible.
OL,17,FAfter a short pursuit, one of Bell's
OL,18,Fdogs, named Titan and described in the
OL,19,Fcharge as "an American bully XL",
OL,20,Fgrabbed Mr Langley by the throat and
OL,21,Fcaused catastrophic injuries.
