OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fsaid he died a short time later after
OL,8,Flosing a significant amount of blood.
OL,10,FPolice shot the dog at the scene to
OL,11,Fprotect the public and it was
OL,12,Funderstood at the time of the attack
OL,13,Fthat another XL bully was taken away
OL,14,Fby police for public safety.
OL,16,FNeighbours said Mr Langley, who was
OL,17,Foriginally from Liverpool, was walking
OL,18,Fhis Patterdale puppy called Bow when
OL,19,Fhe was attacked.
