OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FHis puppy bolted and managed to escape
OL,7,Fand was being looked after by a
OL,8,Fneighbour in the aftermath of the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FTracey, one of Ian Langley's
OL,12,Fneighbours, told ITV Tyne Tees he was
OL,13,F'covered in blood' and couldn't talk
OL,14,Fas she paid tribute to him
OL,16,FOne of Mr Langley's neighbours,
OL,17,FTracey, told ITV Tyne Tees that she
OL,18,Foffered first aid before paramedics
OL,19,Farrived.
