OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FRecalling the attack, she said: "Two
OL,7,Fof my children heard a scream and then
OL,8,FI went out, I knew instantly who it
OL,9,Fwas, he got up and walked towards me.
OL,11,F"He was covered from the neck down in
OL,12,Fblood. He couldn't talk, he was just
OL,13,Fgargling. I made him sit down and I
OL,14,Fput pressure on his neck.
OL,16,F"I was just talking to him, when
OL,17,Fsomebody is in that predicament you
OL,18,Fjust want to remind them of something
OL,19,Fso I was talking about his son.
