OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,F"I've known him for years. He was a
OL,7,Fproud dad and a lovely lad, he never
OL,8,Fharmed anybody."
OL,10,FSince the attack, and following a
OL,11,Fnumber of other attacks by XL Bully
OL,12,Fdogs around the country, the breed is
OL,13,Fnow banned in this country.
OL,15,FSince February 2024 it has been a
OL,16,Fcriminal offence to own an XL Bully
OL,17,Fwithout an exemption certificate.
OL,19,FThe dogs must also be kept on a lead
OL,20,Fand muzzled in public places, as well
OL,21,Fas neutered.
